PrecisAmendment to the TRADE MARKS REGULATIONS deleting references pertaining to the Registered User (a person authorized to use a trade-mark owned by another person or establishment) relating to correspondence, entries in the Trade-marks Journal, the filing of an application for a person as a Registered User and related fees, bringing the Regulations into conformity with the recently enacted Intellectual Property Law Improvement Act.
